Interface AppointmentOutcomeRecordCtrl

All Known Implementing Classes:
DoctorCtrl, PharmacistCtrl
public interface AppointmentOutcomeRecordCtrl
Interface for managing appointment outcome records. Provides methods to view and update the records of appointment outcomes.
